                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title" style="font-size:xx-large;">UofL Honors Program</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">The Honors Program provides students with the best of both worlds in terms of college experience: the intimacy of a small college combined with the vast resources of a national research institution.</p>
                        <p class="card-text">Whether working side-by-side with faculty on cutting edge research projects, exploring international destinations, or serving the local community, Honors students have the chance to participate in unparalleled learning opportunities.</p>
                        <p class="card-text">Honors students may major in any undergraduate program in the university and are required to take at least one Honors course per year as well as maintain a 3.35 GPA.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Go to UofL Honors Portal</a>
                    </div>
